<font color=orange>- 피터 세퍼 -
<font color=yellow>아마데우스</font>

18
00:03:19,887 --> 00:03:22,958
<font color=yellow>F. 머레이 아브라함</font>

19
00:03:29,449 --> 00:03:32,415
<font color=yellow>톰 헐쓰</font>

20
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:36,284
<font color=yellow>엘리자베스 베리지</font>

21
00:03:43,788 --> 00:03:46,985
<font color=yellow>음악(지휘,감독) : 네빌 마리너</font>

22
00:03:47,606 --> 00:03:50,380
<font color=yellow>음악진행 : 존 스트라우스</font>

23
